Reasoning: The paper deals with optimization of transmission schemes for the Gaussian MIMO cognitive radio channel, which involves topics related to information theory (cs.IT), communication systems (cs.COMM), networked systems (cs.NI), control and systems engineering (cs.SY), and multimedia (cs.MM). The use of Dirty Paper Coding (DPC) and the optimization of the sum-rate over transmit covariance matrices are also relevant to these sub-categories.
